Class LinkedBag<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • LinkedBag<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BagInterface<T>

    public class LinkedBag<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements BagInterface<T>
    A class of bags whose entries are stored in a chain of linked nodes. The bag is never full.
